  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to assess the safety, tolerability, antiviral effects, and
      pharmacokinetics of PPI-461 in patients with chronic hepatitis C virus genotype 1 infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
